snippet.textDisplay: China is the most fancy and beautiful place for my traveling around asia. This is a high-quality country keeping the best balance about the environment, living standard, convenience, scenery, price. You can enjoy the modern city, the clean and quiet countryside, the wide grassland, the high-altitude snowy mountains, the endless bamboo sea, the clear lakes and the beautiful desert. Whether from the city or the countryside, the facilities are very complete. Another such country is Japan, but the prices in Japan are relatively high, and the scenery is not so diversified. I also like Japan very much. Although I have returned to my home country, I have always missed life in China and the electric bicycle I stayed there.
